What a spectacular view of the ocean from the top! Do make an effort to climb up the steps. You won't regret it.
It's a clean and secluded beach. Popular for cockle hunting. But check if there's any e-coli outbreak.

Generous portion of pho but a tad oily.

Hot chocolate!

Try the prawn noodles, fish head noodles and sambal petai sotong rice. A tad pricey but at least the portion is good.
